{"tid":549453,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一名女子報稱懷疑在港鐵閘機觸電　警方列雜項事件處理","createTime":"2018-02-03T15:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T15:40:58.000Z","uid":29093,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"043e330a579bf9c914762627e771bb5850d4bc8a","tid":549453,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T15:33:48.000Z","msg":"一名女子報稱傍晚在港鐵大圍站，插入車票出閘時，懷疑手指觸電。警員到場調查，事主並無表面傷痕，其後送院檢查，案件列為雜項事件處理。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵回覆查詢時表示，事後已檢查有關閘機，運作正常。港鐵指，職員收到求助後，已即時協助及報警，並安排該名女子到車站休息室等候救護車，她當時沒有表面傷痕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   傻人發現案  處理算啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n冬天觸電有幾出奇呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1102fb933cab02c6656e5af0b775daca8ac5d1","tid":549453,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T15:38:30.000Z","msg":"靜電咋？"},{"pid":"91da225867acb93530576443ac8bb86e866a7087","tid":549453,"uid":45551,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T15:39:17.000Z","msg":"女人"},{"pid":"a6be068c3a69c2dff5cb071e05f4ab4cdecdc55d","tid":549453,"uid":57003,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T15:39:37.000Z","msg":"想屈錢"},{"pid":"cd7117f1b8891533357ab990b7f5cf731e5ef547","tid":549453,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab1102fb933cab02c6656e5af0b775daca8ac5d1","tid":549453,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T15:38:30.000Z","msg":"靜電咋？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-0